<h3 class="stdHeader">Instant and automated customer notifications</h3>

<p>What if you were able to drastically cut the amount of time you spent on the phone with your customers? Prefiniti makes this a possibility with its customer notification system. Based on the personal preferences of your customers, they will be notified by email or text to a mobile device of the status of their order throughout every stage of the process. Customers are also automatically notified anytime a new file is placed within their order, such as PDF files and invoices. When your customers are receiving constant feedback regarding their business with you, they are happy and you avoid wasting your valuable time on the phone. Just another way Prefiniti helps you run a more efficient business.</p>
